    "= E q θ 2 (z|y) log p(y|z) -E q θ 2 (c|y)q θ 2 (u) D KL (q θ 2 (z| y)||p(z|u, c; σ)).",
    "The same conditional prior p(z|c, u; σ) is applied across the joint and view-specific ELBOs.",
    "We find the {q θ, q θ 1, q θ 2 } that maximize ℒ total by running stochastic gradient descent.",
    "The Starfysh model is implemented as a Python package using PyTorch 85 with the Adam 86 optimizer.",
